ment.uk/resources/1124527/answer",,,,,"21","Northern Ireland","Northern Ireland","2019-05-02","Domestic Abuse Bill (Draft): Northern Ireland","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Northern Ireland, pursuant to the Answer of 25 April 2019 to Question 245778 on Domestic Abuse Bill (Draft): Northern Ireland, if she will provide further details on what new Domestic Abuse Offence in Northern Ireland she is working on with the Home Office and Ministry of justice including publishing any consultation papers for this purpose.","false","Biography information for Stella Creasy","Walthamstow","Stella Creasy","250456"
