"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124615","Cabinet Office","false","2019-05-09","<p>The information requested falls within the responsibility of the UK Statistics Authority. I have asked the Authority to reply.</p>","Torbay","Kevin Foster",,"2019-05-09T09:46:40.287Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124615/answer","Biography information for Kevin Foster","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124615/answer","PQ 250448 (1).pdf","PQ 250448 (1).pdf","UKSA Response","UKSA Response","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124615/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2019-05-02","Employment: Disability","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, what recent assessment he has made of the percentage of employed individuals with long-term disablities who are employed in (a) higher managerial, administrative and professional occupations and (b) routine occupations.","false","Biography information for Chris Ruane","Vale of Clwyd","Chris Ruane","250448"
