"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124206","Ministry of Justice","false","2019-05-13","<p>The number of defendants prosecuted and offenders found guilty of offences under Sections 4 to 8 of the Animal Welfare Act 2006, in the Metropolitan Police Force area and the North East London local justice area, from 2012 to 2017, can be viewed in the table. Information specifically related to Romford is not available so the North East London Local Justice Area (which includes Romford) has been provided.</p><p> </p><p>Court proceedings and cautions data for 2018 is planned for publication on 16 May 2019.</p>","South Swindon","Robert Buckland",,"2019-05-13T16:18:24.327Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124206/answer","Biography information for Robert Buckland","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124206/answer","Copy of PQ 249875 table.xlsx","Copy of PQ 249875 table.xlsx","Table","Table","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124206/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2019-05-01","Animal Welfare: Romford","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many animal cruelty (a) offences and (b) convictions there were in Romford constituency in each year since 2012.","false","Biography information for Andrew Rosindell","Romford","Andrew Rosindell","249875"
