"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124365","Department for Exiting the European Union ","false","2019-05-08","<p>No contracts have been entered into with Emerdata Limited in the last year.</p>","Spelthorne","Kwasi Kwarteng",,"2019-05-08T10:57:12.133Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124365/answer","Biography information for Kwasi  Kwarteng","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124365/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124365/answer",,,,,"203","Exiting the European Union ","Exiting the European Union ","2019-05-01","Department for Exiting the European Union: Emerdata","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Exiting the European Union, whether (a) his Department, (b) his Department's agencies and (c) his Department's associated public bodies have entered into contracts with Emerdata Limited in the last year.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre Brock","250042"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124366","Department for International Trade","false","2019-05-08","<p>The Department for International Trade (DIT) has not held any contracts with Emerdata Limited in the last year. DIT does not currently have any agencies or public bodies.</p>","Meon Valley","George Hollingbery",,"2019-05-08T11:51:33.477Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124366/answer","Biography information for Sir George Hollingbery","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124366/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/1124366/answer",,,,,"202","International Trade","International Trade","2019-05-01","Department for International Trade: Emerdata","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Trade, whether (a) his Department, (b) his Department's agencies and (c) his Department's associated public bodies have entered into contracts with Emerdata Limited in the last year.","false","Biography information for Deidre Brock","Edinburgh North and Leith","Deidre Brock","250043"
